>> time required: 20 minites
>> course: side

Rinse @basmati rice{1.5%cups} until runs clear, drain set aside
In a pan add @butter{1/4%cup} and start to brown,
Add dried @egg noodles{0.5%cups}, and rice
Then add minced @garlic cloves{2}
When rice is white, add boiling @water{3%cups}, @allspice{1%tsp}, and powdered @chicken stock{2%tsp}
Bring to boil, cover and simmer for ~{15minutes}
